
FIRST DISTRIBUTION VERSION.  MPI FFT for mean fields.

Velocity gauge sinc DVR just implemented, not debugged nor checked for factors.

MPI ORBITAL PARALLELIZATION for sinc dvr (chmctdhf_sinc) only with parorbsplit=3.
  set both parorbsplit=3 in &parinp and orbparflag=.true. in &sinc_params

On Mac: minimal demonstration

1)   cd ~/myprogs/LBNL-AMO-MCTDHF
     git clone https://github.com/LBNL-AMO-MCTDHF/V1.0BETA.030315.INTELFFT
     cd V1.0BETA.030315.INTELFFT
     mv COMPDIRS/*mac* .
     rm -r COMPDIRS

2A)  cd BIN.ecs.hermorm.mac
     ./Makeme
2B)  cd BIN.ecs.hermorm.mac.mpi
     ./Makeme

3A)  cd ../EXAMPLES/METHANE.abs.0.40186.45pts
     ln -s ../../BIN.ecs.hermnorm/chmctdhf_sinc ./chmctdhf_sinc
     ./chmctdhf_sinc Inp=Input.Inp.Relax | tee Outs/Out.relax
     ./chmctdhf_sinc Inp=Input.Inp.Pulse | tee Outs/Out.pulse
     ./gnu.abs.here
3B)  cd ../EXAMPLES/METHANE.abs.0.40186.45pts
     ln -s ../../BIN.ecs.hermnorm.mpi/chmctdhf_sinc ./chmctdhf_sinc.mpi
     mpirun -n 15 ./chmctdhf_sinc.mpi Inp=Input.Inp.Relax | tee Outs/Out.relax
     mpirun -n 15 ./chmctdhf_sinc.mpi Inp=Input.Inp.Pulse | tee Outs/Out.pulse
     ./gnu.abs.here

  DJH 03-07-2015

